<template><ModulePageShell title="麻醉专业质控指标" description="服务端权威计算、证据口径与病例穿透"><template #toolbar><a-space><a-select v-model="category" style="width:140px"><a-option value="全部">全部</a-option><a-option value="structure">结构</a-option><a-option value="process">过程</a-option><a-option value="outcome">结果</a-option><a-option value="pacu">PACU</a-option><a-option value="postoperative">术后</a-option><a-option value="obstetric">产科</a-option></a-select><a-button :loading="loading" @click="reload">查询</a-button></a-space></template><a-alert v-if="error" type="error" show-icon>{{error}}</a-alert><a-empty v-else-if="!loading&&!indicators.length" description="当前范围无可计算指标"/><a-card v-else class="section-card" :bordered="false" title="26项指标"><a-table :data="indicators" row-key="code" :pagination="{pageSize:10}"><a-table-column title="编码" data-index="code"/><a-table-column title="指标" data-index="name"/><a-table-column title="分子/分母"><template #cell="{record}">{{record.numerator}} / {{record.denominator}}</template></a-table-column><a-table-column title="当前值" data-index="displayValue"/><a-table-column title="状态"><template #cell="{record}"><a-tag :color="color(record.status)">{{record.status}}</a-tag></template></a-table-column><a-table-column title="口径"><template #cell="{record}"><a-link @click="openDetail(record)">查看证据</a-link></template></a-table-column></a-table></a-card><a-drawer v-model:visible="visible" width="720px" :title="selected?.name"><template v-if="selected"><a-descriptions :column="1" bordered><a-descriptions-item label="分母">{{selected.denominatorDefinition}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="分子">{{selected.numeratorDefinition}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="排除">{{selected.exclusions.join('；')}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="时间窗">{{selected.timeWindow.anchor}} / {{selected.timeWindow.granularity}} / {{selected.timeWindow.timezone}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="证据">{{selected.evidenceFields.join('；')}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="严重度">{{selected.severity}}</a-descriptions-item><a-descriptions-item label="整改动作">{{selected.remediationAction}}</a-descriptions-item></a-descriptions><a-divider>病例穿透</a-divider><a-spin :loading="detailLoading"><a-table :data="detail?.defectCases ?? []" :pagination="false"><a-table-column title="病例ID" data-index="caseId"/><a-table-column title="患者" data-index="patientName"/><a-table-column title="手术" data-index="operationName"/><a-table-column title="缺陷" data-index="defectDesc"/></a-table></a-spin></template></a-drawer></ModulePageShell></template>
<script setup lang="ts">import{onMounted,ref}from'vue';import ModulePageShell from'@/components/shared/ModulePageShell.vue';import{qualityApi,type QualityIndicatorApi,type QualityIndicatorDetailApi}from'@/api/quality';import type{QualityCategory}from'@/types/quality';const category=ref<'全部'|QualityCategory>('全部'),indicators=ref<QualityIndicatorApi[]>([]),selected=ref<QualityIndicatorApi|null>(null),detail=ref<QualityIndicatorDetailApi|null>(null),loading=ref(false),detailLoading=ref(false),error=ref(''),visible=ref(false);const color=(s:string)=>s==='normal'?'green':s==='warning'?'orange':s==='abnormal'?'red':'gray';async function reload(){loading.value=true;error.value='';try{indicators.value=await qualityApi.getIndicators({category:category.value});}catch(e){indicators.value=[];error.value=`加载失败：${(e as Error).message}`;}finally{loading.value=false;}}async function openDetail(row:QualityIndicatorApi){selected.value=row;detail.value=null;visible.value=true;detailLoading.value=true;try{detail.value=await qualityApi.getIndicatorDetail(row.code,{category:category.value});}catch(e){error.value=`穿透失败：${(e as Error).message}`;}finally{detailLoading.value=false;}}onMounted(reload);</script>
